    li "Exactly. If we go this week, then Hanako won't be able to make the link."

    hi "Very crafty. I'll meet you at the gate. What time should I get there?"

    li "Let's see, the first bus leaves at nine on a Sunday, but I think that is a little early."

    li "How about ten?"

